  "key": "C major",
  "genre": [
    "Ballad",
    "Ambient"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 4,
  "lyrics": "Here we go. Can you feel the connection between me and you and the groove? But you said there's no surface, no mouth, no connection past what you see in this reality. Baby, you know we can get higher than that, higher than that. Oh, you know that we can get higher than that, higher than that. There's gotta be connection to the one you dream of yourself. It's not just you and us, it's in the inside of your mind. Baby, can't just come to the top of us all. So, don't get like it's broken, it's not. You're already spoken for inside the soul of your life. Don't forget that there's more, there's more, there's more, there's more. There's still time for you to get yourself back on. Just gotta repay the, just gotta repay the reconnect fee and like taxes and anything. Baby, that's why there's no surface for you. Don't let no surface out to you. Got corporate time taking everything from my hands. Can't even have community events. Somebody's gonna say we're looking back to you. And you're a mistake, but then you've done it too. Cause we're not losing anything here. We're not missing anything in this. Cause we're not missing anything from the people that tell you to not love yourself. And the people that tell you that you're not good enough. Hope you don't have that connection, baby. There's no surface for you.",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 24.940000534057617,
      "text": "Here we go.",
      "start": 23.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 66.72000122070312,
      "text": "Can you feel the connection between me and you and the groove?",
      "start": 55.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 75.08000183105469,
      "text": "But you said there's no surface, no mouth, no connection past what you see in this reality.",
      "start": 68.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 80.94000244140625,
      "text": "Baby, you know we can get higher than that, higher than that.",
      "start": 75.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 87.58000183105469,
      "text": "Oh, you know that we can get higher than that, higher than that.",
      "start": 81.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 92.13999938964844,
      "text": "There's gotta be connection to the one you dream of yourself.",
      "start": 87.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 96.69999694824219,
      "text": "It's not just you and us, it's in the inside of your mind.",
      "start": 92.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 100.87999725341797,
      "text": "Baby, can't just come to the top of us all.",
      "start": 96.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 103.9800033569336,
      "text": "So, don't get like it's broken, it's not.",
      "start": 101.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 107.12000274658203,
      "text": "You're already spoken for inside the soul of your life.",
      "start": 104.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 112.91999816894531,
      "text": "Don't forget that there's more, there's more, there's more, there's more.",
      "start": 107.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 117.33999633789062,
      "text": "There's still time for you to get yourself back on.",
      "start": 113.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 124.37999725341797,
      "text": "Just gotta repay the, just gotta repay the reconnect fee and like taxes and anything.",
      "start": 117.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 130.72000122070312,
      "text": "Baby, that's why there's no surface for you.",
      "start": 124.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 136.72000122070312,
      "text": "Don't let no surface out to you.",
      "start": 130.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 141.25999450683594,
      "text": "Got corporate time taking everything from my hands.",
      "start": 137.83999633789062
    },
